{
  "texts": [
    "A dropout layer was then included as a regularization method to avoid overfitting.",
    "The hybrid neural network composed of MLP and GRU is introduced in the proposed work.",
    "Electricity consumption data is used as input into the proposed GRU-MLP network.",
    "The proposed methodology was motivated by research for identifying electricity theft done in (Cheng et al., 2021).",
    "The research in (Xu et al., 2018) generated the LSTM-MLP hybrid neural network classifier."
  ]
}